title: Live from Eugene, Oregon, previewing Top Matchups for Week 8
description:
Live from Eugene, Oregon, Jen Lada, David Pollack and Desmond Howard dive into the Week 8 ranked CFB matchups. They take deep looks Oregon vs UCLA, Syracuse vs Clemson, and Kansas State vs TCU. Additionally, they discuss OSU's quarterback Spencer Sander's status for this week's matchup vs Texas, as well as a look into Oregon's tight end who passed this summer, Spencer Webb. Alabama's bounce back matchup vs Mississippi State is also discussed.
